### 5. How to Run on Android Emulator (after SDK install)

```bash
# Start emulator in Android Studio, then:
dotnet run -f net10.0-android --project mobile/VinhKhanh.Mobile

# Or build APK:
dotnet build -f net10.0-android -c Debug
# APK at: mobile/VinhKhanh.Mobile/bin/Debug/net10.0-android/com.vinhkhanh.foodtour-Signed.apk
```

For API access from emulator, backend must be running on host port 5015:
```bash
# Backend
dotnet run --project backend/src/VinhKhanh.API

# appsettings.json ApiBaseUrl = "http://10.0.2.2:5015/api/v1"  ‚Üê emulator ‚Üí host
```

